Beatrice Colen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beatrice_Colen 0 Beatrice Colen (January 10, 1948 - November 18, 1999) was an American actress. Her most famous roles were Marsha Simms on Happy Days and Etta Candy on Wonder Woman. Beatrice_Colen ( January_10_,_1948 - November_18_,_1999 ) was an_American_actress .
